            <title>[SEC-963] LDAP Namespace Group Search Base Should Default to Directory Root</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-963</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Group search base cannot be set to root when spring security is configured to authenticate against an LDAP directory using the namespace style config. Please see the thread below for more details.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=55303&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=55303&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows XP, Tomcat 6 and Java 6 with lotus domino LDAP directory</environment>
